@EFSearch.Sample.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5292

### Get all products (paginated)
GET {{EFSearch.Sample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products?pageNumber=1&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

### Get product by ID
GET {{EFSearch.Sample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products/1
Accept: application/json

### Search products - Filter by category
POST {{EFSearch.Sample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filters": [
    {
      "field": "CategoryName",
      "operator": "Equals",
      "value": "Electronics"
    }
  ],
  "sorts": [],
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### Search products - Filter by price range and sort by price descending
POST {{EFSearch.Sample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filters": [
    {
      "field": "Price",
      "operator": "LessThanOrEqual",
      "value": 100
    }
  ],
  "sorts": [
    {
      "field": "Price",
      "direction": "Descending"
    }
  ],
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### Search products - Filter by name contains "Desk"
POST {{EFSearch.Sample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filters": [
    {
      "field": "Name",
      "operator": "Contains",
      "value": "Desk"
    }
  ],
  "sorts": [
    {
      "field": "Name",
      "direction": "Ascending"
    }
  ],
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### Search products - Filter active products only, sorted by CreatedAt
POST {{EFSearch.Sample.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filters": [
    {
      "field": "IsActive",
      "operator": "Equals",
      "value": true
    }
  ],
  "sorts": [
    {
      "field": "CreatedAt",
      "direction": "Descending"
    }
  ],
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "pageSize": 5
}

